layers.nm: One of A.I.s biggest risk factor is when they interpret bad data. If there isnt well curated collections of data for training A.I., corrupt data can be formed and could potentially be fatal.

s.t: One of A.I.s biggest risk factors is when they interpret bad data. If there isnt well curated collections of data for training A.I., corrupt data can be formed and could potentially be fatal.

layers.nm: An example of this occuring is when Google had to censor image searches for keywords like "gorilla" and "chimp" because it returned photos of African-Americans.
